B.I1=new A.ci("sector_neg_finance",'Finance sector rattled as central bank raises rates to "make money more expensive, somehow"','The Federal Reserve raised its benchmark rate by 50 basis points and issued a statement that economists described as "technically a sentence." Banking stocks fell on margin pressure fears.',-7,-2,"Finance",!1)
B.I8=new A.ci("sector_neg_tech","Tech sector slumps after regulator learns what an algorithm is",'Regulators launched investigations into tech companies after a committee member Googled "what is software" and became alarmed. Sentiment darkened across the sector pending a follow-up Google.',-6,-2,"Technology",!1)
