B.HY=new A.ci("sector_neg_consumer","Consumer sector slumps as people remember they can just not buy things","Consumer spending came in well below forecasts after a widely shared social media post reminded people that saving money is also an option. Discretionary stocks fell sharply.",-5,-2,"Consumer",!1)
